Rating: 4
I made this mango sesame dressing to top my chicken. I found it absolutely delicious. Great and has many uses for asian foods. However, I did make a few substitutions i really recommend. First, a family member is allergic to mango, so we switch the mango chutney for a combination of peach preserves and apricot chutney. It was amazing. Also, I added about 1/4 cup more peach preserves than was recommended. Gave it an amazing flavor. Overall, it was fabulous.

