Rating: 4
Deeeeelicious. I used olive oil instead of cooking or canola and it was really good. Also, I used seasoned rice vinegar and it also worked out just fine. For those that may be worried that this dressing could be too sweet or mango-y, don't worry. It was savory and tangy, and I did not find the mango to be too 'in your face'. It was great - highly recommended!